{
  "stem": "15115.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 27.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I start crying because I knew what was going on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I went to my kapo, can you help him?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Please.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My brother, they took the number.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So they went over here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They went to the block at-- so the guy was in charge of this particular block.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He went to him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He was a nice Gentile-- my kapo was a nice man, a handsome man.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He went to this guy, he says, listen, this number so and so, 114192.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Takes a look and says, yeah, the number is gone already.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He went to the-- to the [GERMAN], it was the office, you know, the German-- couldn't do nothing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in the middle of the night, midnight, 12:00, they took him on foot, which is the worst thing, you know.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When my parents got burned and killed, they didn't know if they were coming or going.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, they just went to take a bath, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, in 10-- 10, 15, 20 minutes were all dead.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But those people, they took them on foot to-- to the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was the worst thing anybody know already.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "By that time, we knew what those chimneys was, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We knew exactly what the chimneys-- so and then before they got into the doors from the crematorium, a lot of people wouldn't want to go in.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they shot them in the doorways, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "All around so we-- we found out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So that's when I lost my brother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But prior to that, my older-- my second brother was a selection.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But that selection was to take some workers to-- what do you call it-- to another camp, Camp Buna, the name Buna.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So he was selected.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I was not selected.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I lost my brother.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
